: "Media Stereotypes", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Media_Stereotypes?f_ri=72282"}]}, {"id": 51022514, "title": "As armadilhas do \"hor\u00e1rio nobre \u00e9 o meu\"", "created_at": "2021-08-26T15:27:32.878-07:00", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/51022514/As_armadilhas_do_hor%C3%A1rio_nobre_%C3%A9_o_meu_?f_ri=72282", "dom_id": "work_51022514", "summary": "O consumo ass\u00edncrono de fic\u00e7\u00e3o televisiva, facilitado pelo modelo de distribui\u00e7\u00e3o de conte\u00fado sob demanda, criou novos h\u00e1bitos de ver TV e coloca em pr\u00e1tica a previs\u00e3o feita por Negroponte, em 1995, de que na televis\u00e3o do futuro o \u201chor\u00e1rio nobre\u201d seria determinado pela audi\u00eancia. Este trabalho pretende fazer uma discuss\u00e3o sobre como o novo fluxo de produ\u00e7\u00e3o, circula\u00e7\u00e3o e recep\u00e7\u00e3o leva a um embate entre temporalidades e provoca um certo mal-estar pelo excesso de op\u00e7\u00f5es e liberdade existentes hoje.", "downloadable_attachments": [{"id": 68893946, "asset_id": 51022514, "asset_type": "Work", "always_allow_download": false}], "ordered_authors": [{"id": 36877351, "first_name": "Vanessa", "last_name": "Scalei", "domain_name": "pucrs", "page_name": "VanessaScalei", "display_name": "Vanessa Scalei", "profile_url": "https://pucrs.academia.edu/VanessaScalei?f_ri=72282", "photo": "https://0.academia-photos.com/36877351/12577366/51236740/s65_vanessa.scalei.jpg"}], "research_interests": [{"id": 1571, "name": "Television Studies", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Television_Studies?f_ri=72282", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 72282, "name": "Television Consumption", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Television_Consumption?f_ri=72282", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 274431, "name": "TV Series", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/TV_Series?f_ri=72282", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 649723, "name": "Fic\u00e7\u00e3o Seriada Televisiva", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/